reviews.snippet:
東京都新宿区西早稲田の『ムガル』で「コルカタビリヤニセット(チキン)」を食す。

店内はまさに町中のインド料理店と言った感じ。
それだけに東インドコルカタ出身のシェフが手掛ける料理は本格的。
特に“コルカタビリヤニの特徴は香りを楽しむビリヤニ”と言われているだけに香りを楽しめるのがポイント。
さらにセットのラッシーが感動的においしかったので、このビリヤニとラッシーをもとめてぜひともまた訪れてみたくなるお店。

extracted_snippet.translated:
I had the Kolkata Biryani Set (Chicken) at Mughal in Nishi-Waseda, Shinjuku Ward, Tokyo.

The interior of the restaurant feels like a downtown Indian restaurant.

The food, prepared by a chef from Kolkata in eastern India, is authentic.

It's said that the distinctive feature of Kolkata biryani is that it's a biryani that you can enjoy the aroma of, so the aroma is a highlight.

The lassi that came with the set was also incredibly delicious, so I'd definitely like to return to this restaurant just to try the biryani and lassi.

response.snippet: 口コミをいただき、誠にありがとうございます。コルカタビリヤニの香りを楽しんでいただけて嬉しく思います。特にラッシーについてお褒めいただき光栄です。東インド出身シェフの本格的な料理を楽しんでいただけたようで何よりです。またのご来店を心よりお待ちしております。

すごく美味しかった。
当店のビリヤニですが、鼻に抜けるスパイスの香りを一口目でこれほど感じたことはないです。
驚きました。

サグチキンというカレー、パクチーがたくさん入っていて、これもまた香り豊かなカレーで本当に美味しかった。

早稲田には、あまり来ることはないのですが、リピートしたいお店です。

August 30, 2025
It was absolutely delicious.
This restaurant's biryani had such a strong spice aroma that it hit me right from the first bite.
I was amazed.

The saag chicken curry was packed with cilantro, and it was also incredibly fragrant and delicious.

I don't come to Waseda very often, but this is a restaurant I'd like to return to.

extracted_snippet.translated:
On this day, I ordered chicken biryani ☀️
I was already happy from the moment the aroma of spices rose...
The rice was light and fluffy, yet packed with flavor—authentic! ✨
The chicken was tender and fell apart, perfectly complemented by the spices! ️

The accompanying yogurt sauce (raita) is a nice accent!❣
It mellows out the spiciness, so you won't get bored of it until the very end.☺️

The restaurant is bustling with students and regulars, and it's a very comfortable place.◎
It's great that you can enjoy not only curry but also authentic biryani for lunch.♥️

Recommended for those wanting to get into an ethnic atmosphere in Waseda.♬

The handsome staff really get you excited.🙊💖

*+:･｡☆｡･:+*ﾟ

✧ Business Hours: 11:00 AM - 3:00 PM / 5:00 PM - 11:00 PM
✧ Closed: Open daily
✧ Access: 5-minute walk from Waseda Station on the Tokyo Metro Tozai Line
